<% configured_description = ReSetting.get_serialized('re_user_profile', @project.id)['description']%>
<% if configured_description.blank? %> 
	<p>You can use user profiles to describe your users.</p>
	<p>Describing the stakeholder with user profiles is are very
        important because all requirements come from people. Thus you should
        discover and document all stakeholder which are involved in your project.'
        <!--#  Taken from: [Alexander 2009, S 28]--></p>
<% else %> 
	<%= textilizable(configured_description, :only_path => false) %> 
<% end %> 

